headline: JPMorgan starts coverage on SMID Industirals, says it’s ’time to be bullish now’
summary: Investing.com -- JPMorgan has begun coverage on five small and mid-cap (SMID) industrial stocks with a bullish view, arguing that safety is emerging as a central driver of growth.
